---
title: Roast Veg Rigatoni with pomodoro sauce and cheese
description: This veg-filled pasta dish is the perfect plate for when you want something that's quick to make and will make you feel good. Al dente linguine and an array of veg mean this is a meal that's satisfying while also being suitably healthy.
